longBusinessSummary: Hong Kong Winalite Group, Inc. engages in marketing and selling personal health and hygiene products in the People's Republic of China and internationally. Its products consist of ultra-thin regular anionic and long anionic sanitary pads, anionic pantiliners, and baby diapers. The company also provides consulting, management, technical, marketing, financial, and other services to its distributors; and licenses the Winalite mark and brand to the manufacturers and distributors of its products. It procures goods that it sells from an independent manufacturer in mainland China and sells them through contracted direct-selling distributors, and wholesale and retail establishments. The company was founded in 2007 and is based in Mongkok, Hong Kong.
